      Title: Revelations
      Locus: XI
    Commentary: The names Elias and Enoch are witnesses to the events
      chronicled in Revelations.
---
Elias and Enoch wandered from India to the sea, each followed by a great band
who were all Christians and fled to them from Anti-Christ.
